    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been absolute gold. It\u2019s been super well-loved and runs like a dream, perfect for anyone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great in the driveway. It\u2019s been kept in really solid shape and is totally ready for its next adventure with you! Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re gonna love how it handles!",
